summary:
Hi there, thanks for checking out my profile! I'm Filip - a Non-Financial Risk Manager at NN Bank where I use my business analytics skills to tackle data-heavy Non Financial Risk (NFR) projects. Apart from data management and analytics, I have a knack for academic research in the field of behavioral finance and am known to sometimes dabble in graphic design projects using Adobe Illustrator, InDesign and Photoshop.

As a student I've had the opportunity to travel to 20+ European countries whilst participating in various programs, summer schools, and competitions. During that period I gathered valuable experience working at diverse companies - from marketing agencies to large financial institutions. Upon finishing my Master's degree in Banking and Finance at Utrecht University, I joined a highly dynamic team at ABN AMRO (Risk Data & Analytics) and later NN Bank (Non-Financial Risk) where I got the chance to combine my technical and professional skills in tackling topics such as fraud analysis, data migration, data dashboarding & visualization, control testing, and regulatory compliance. Moreover, I’m currently involved with multiple projects within the NN Young Talent Group and Club Alpbach Croatia - feel free to reach out for more info on these!

Specialties: Non-Financial Risk Management, SQL, Data Management & Analytics, Dashboarding, Business Development, Research, STATA, Creative Thinking, Event Planning and Organizing

Please reach out to me if you'd like to discuss any of the following:
• (Non-Financial) Risk Management Topics 
• Behavioral Finance & Economics
• Data Management & Analytics
• Corporate Social Responsibility Ideas
• Experiences regarding studying in the Netherlands
• Anything videogame related
• Grabbing a (virtual) coffee
• Surprise me!
